{
  "name": "atomic-os",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "private": false,
  "description": "Atomic Operating System — a structured-read + atomic-edit MCP server that closes the Line-Oriented Action Bottleneck for AI CLI agents. Intention high, action minimal, proof clear, rollback possible, continuity persisted, product as the end.",
